  - Petal length range: 2-4 cm
  - Sepal width range: 3-4.5 cm

- Virginica species:
  - Average sepal length: 7.1-7.9 cm
  - Average sepal width: 3.5-4.5 cm
  - Petal width range: 1-2.5 cm
